data.description: Join the Diamante family & savor the unique lifestyle in Hot Spring Village’s only private subdivision.   Move-in ready, recently remodeled with new appliances, flooring & paint.  An open floor plan with an abundance of windows.   Spacious kitchen & walk-in pantry.  A luxurious primary suite, bath and huge walk-in closet.  The laundry room is thoughtfully located off the primary.   The lower level offers a complete living space with living room, kitchen, two bedrooms, & a storm shelter/storage space.  It boasts its own exterior entrance, offering rental potential separate from upstairs.  A wraparound deck & gazebo for enjoying the serene surroundings.   A 3-car garage with ample space for your golf cart or workshop.  A generous corner lot offers views of Diamante #6 green and glimpses of hole #7’s fountain.   Beautiful private golf course & subdivision living in HSV, AR.  Diamante subdivision & country club is home to Golf Digest’s #3 ranked AR golf course.  Club amenities include world class tennis & pickleball, a private swimming pool & wide array of dining & social events.    FURNISHED.
